  (text "ESP32-S3-WROOM-1-N16R8 CO-PROCESSOR NOTES:\\nPSRAM: GPIO35/36/37 consumed internally by 8MB octal PSRAM.\\n  Mark NC on PCB. Do not route signals to these pads.\\nGPIO0 pullup R11 (10kΩ to +3V3): boot-safe. CS_S3_MPU on carrier.\\nEN pullup R10 (10kΩ to +3V3): required, do not omit.\\nUSB CDC/JTAG: GPIO19/20 → J5. Replaces UART0. Debug via USB.\\nSPI2 (display): GPIO17=CLK GPIO18=MOSI GPIO11=CS GPIO16=DC\\nSPI3 (slave): GPIO14=SCK GPIO13=MOSI GPIO12=MISO GPIO10=CS\\nI2C (shared): GPIO8=SDA GPIO9=SCL → ES8388 (0x10) + GT911 (0x5D)\\nWIRELESS: S3 radio UNUSED. C6 handles WiFi/BLE/Thread/Matter/Zigbee."
    (at 30 185 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "a8216fe1-8517-4eb4-a1af-a1bafda0e3ba")
  )
